  "title": "Production Assistant",
  "description": "<h3>Production Assistant</h3><p>We are looking for a Production Assistant to support the Production Supervisor in daily manufacturing operations. The role involves reviewing production schedules, understanding product specifications, preparing and weighing materials, and assisting in the production process. You will also be responsible for completing batch records and ensuring all production documentation is accurate and timely.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum GCE ‘O’ Level</p></li><li><p>Detail-oriented and willing to learn</p></li><li><p>Able to work in a manufacturing environment</p></li></ul><p><strong>Interested applicants, please submit your resume in MS Word format to:</strong></p><p>ivytan@jobally.com.sg</p><p>EA Licence No. 18C9228 | Registration No. R1108261 (Tan Li Tze)</p><p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p>",
